    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cupboard in which the archives are kept. An inscription sometimes indicates its function. The term is often used to refer to the archives of a church, confraternity, or a town.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
